  "special": {
    "title": "Evil will be SMASHED!!! WITH SMASHING!!! EVIL!!! SMASH!!! ER!!!",
    "description": "Shots explode on impact, dealing 90% grenade-type splash damage. Each reload has a 7% chance to buff the next magazine: +900% damage, +100% projectile speed, +60% fire rate, +17 mag size, -50% max inaccuracy, +200% max accuracy, +200% recoil recovery, -150% recoil, -200% spread. Assault rifles (except Jakobs) have -20% crit damage scaling."
  },
  "notes": "Like other Torgue rifles, its shots explode on impact and gain bonus splash that scales with grenade-damage bonuses. That splash is applied after internal calculations, so effects like Anarchy do not boost it, while outside modifiers such as Death Mark do. The reload power-up can rarely chain and stack the stat boost. Magazine-size changes from skills or class mods affect both the base and buffed versions, and because the proc happens before the reload finishes, you can cancel the reload with melee or weapon swap to retry until it triggers. An old buff glitch can still be abused while Gunzerking.",
